snippet.title: Xenoblade Chronicles 3 Expansion Pass - Volume 3 - Nintendo Direct 2.8.23
snippet.description:
Say hello to Masha, the newest Hero coming to Xenoblade Chronicles 3 as part of the Expansion Pass. Volume 3 arrives 2/15!

Volume 3 will also include a new rouge-like inspired Challenge Battles mode where you can unlock special-in-game outfits!

And coming in Volume 4 later this year…
